Localization.Name: Get Up Coffee  (Milk)
Localization.Description:
HEI: 15
Effects: Dehydrating, Cognitive Boosting

Get Up Coffee is roasted with care to ensure a smooth blend of rich coffee flavor brewed to perfection. A splash of milk rounds out the flavor and emphasizes its natural sweetness.
